HEADWORD: Aëromancy
<hw>A"⟦eum⟧r*o*man`cy</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>A⟦eum⟧ro-</ets> + <ets>-mancy</ets>: cf. F.
